import React from 'react'
import { Offcanvas, } from 'react-bootstrap'

function LeftBar({ show }) {
    return (
        <Offcanvas show={show} placement='start' autoFocus backdrop keyboard >
            <Offcanvas.Header closeButton >
                <Offcanvas.Title as="h1">Offcanvas</Offcanvas.Title>
            </Offcanvas.Header>
            <Offcanvas.Body>
                Some text as placeholder. In real life you can have the elements you
                have chosen. Like, text, images, lists, etc.sss
            </Offcanvas.Body>
        </Offcanvas>
    )
}

export default LeftBar
